"title": "5963: sympathy",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5963",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The ability to appreciate another's condition, especially through shared experience of pain or suffering. God sympathises with his people in their sufferings, as does Jesus Christ as the sympathetic high priest.</p>\n<h2>God sympathises with his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:14\">PSA 10:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3-2Cor1:4\">2CO 1:3–1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:26-Exod22:27\">EXO 22:26–22:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:18\">DEU 10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:18\">JDG 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:9\">PSA 9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:15\">PSA 91:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:1-Isa40:2\">ISA 40:1–40:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:13\">ISA 66:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:18\">JER 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:6\">2CO 7:6</a></p>\n<h2>God's apparent lack of sympathy may be evidence of judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:5-Jer16:6\">JER 16:5–16:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa27:11\">ISA 27:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:15\">ISA 63:15</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ sympathises with those in distress</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:35\">JHN 11:35</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15\">HEB 4:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:36\">MAT 9:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:41\">MRK 1:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:34\">LUK 7:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14-Heb2:18\">HEB 2:14–2:18</a></p>\n<h2>Sympathy as a characteristic of friendship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:34\">1SA 20:34</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:11\">JOB 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:37\">JDG 11:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:41\">1SA 20:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:2-2Sam10:3\">2SA 10:2–10:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr19:2-1Chr19:3\">1CH 19:2–19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:4-Job16:5\">JOB 16:4–16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:21\">JOB 19:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:16\">JOB 29:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:25\">JOB 30:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:10\">ECC 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:9\">DAN 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:18-John11:19\">JHN 11:18–11:19</a></p>\n<h2>Sympathy expected from God's people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:9\">EXO 23:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:15\">ROM 12:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:21\">EXO 22:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:33-Lev19:34\">LEV 19:33–19:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:19\">DEU 10:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:6-Isa58:7\">ISA 58:6–58:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:4-2Cor1:7\">2CO 1:4–1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:7\">2CO 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:29\">2CO 11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:7\">PHP 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1\">PHP 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:14\">PHP 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:11-1Thess2:12\">1TH 2:11–2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:9-1Tim5:10\">1TI 5:9–5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:34\">HEB 10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:3\">HEB 13:3</a></p>\n<h2>The absence of sympathy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:20\">PSA 69:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:7\">DEU 15:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:14-Job6:18\">JOB 6:14–6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:11-Ps31:12\">PSA 31:11–31:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:11\">PSA 38:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:9\">PSA 41:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:10\">JER 20:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:16\">LAM 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:12\">OBA 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:33\">MAT 18:33</a></p>",
